name: BA: Swiftable 2020
about: Swiftable is a brand new iOS conference from Latin America, having the first edition in Buenos Aires. Taking place in "Centro Cultural de la Ciencia" with capacity for 480 attendees, the event will last two days from Nov 28th to Nov 29th. The whole conference will be carried out in English. Being a piece of the Latin American iOS ecosystem, we want to gather all the communities in one place, where people will be able to share knowledge and techniques to improve iOS craftmanship
